00:29:54,215 --> 00:29:55,815
What's wrong?

521
00:29:56,870 --> 00:29:58,700
My mom...

522
00:30:00,630 --> 00:30:03,140
was diagnosed with a tumor.

523
00:30:22,420 --> 00:30:24,600
Is it benign or malignant?

524
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:27,910
We don't know yet.

525
00:30:27,910 --> 00:30:30,470
She needs an operation.

526
00:30:32,910 --> 00:30:37,870
- Do you think my mom would... 
 - It must be benign.

527
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:42,872
Don't scare yourself before you know anything.

528
00:30:42,872 --> 00:30:44,495
Sure.

529
00:30:45,790 --> 00:30:47,250
Yes.

530
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:01,690
Grandma.

531
00:32:08,020 --> 00:32:09,530
It's late.

532
00:32:09,530 --> 00:32:11,700
Why are you still awake?

533
00:32:12,460 --> 00:32:15,210
I'm going through your mom's photo album.

534
00:32:17,070 --> 00:32:21,510
I heard your mom say you made this for her.

535
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:27,303
During high school.

536
00:32:38,020 --> 00:32:42,830
Our Huan Er has grown up, and is sensible.

537
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:51,700
It'll be fine.

538
00:33:02,940 --> 00:33:07,590
 At that moment, I suddenly understood 

539
00:33:07,590 --> 00:33:13,560
 that Grandma and I are keeping the same secret for each other. 

540
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:16,620
 She's a mother. 

541
00:33:16,620 --> 00:33:20,690
 A mother who's willing to pretend that she knows nothing. 

542
00:33:20,690 --> 00:33:25,430
 Because she doesn't want her daughter to worry about her 

543
00:33:25,430 --> 00:33:29,860
 while suffering from illness. 

544
00:34:08,460 --> 00:34:10,611
Mom, this is braised pork knuckle I made for you.

545
00:34:10,611 --> 00:34:12,680
Remember to put it in the refrigerator after you're home.

546
00:34:12,680 --> 00:34:14,270
Or it will go bad.

547
00:34:14,270 --> 00:34:16,980
This is a new type of diabetes medication.

548
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:19,910
I've written out the instructions for you.

549
00:34:19,910 --> 00:34:22,200
How many times a day, how many pills each time.

550
00:34:22,200 --> 00:34:23,670
Got it.

551
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:26,060
I'm not senile yet.

552
00:34:26,060 --> 00:34:32,080
Mom, I have to rush to work and still need to clean up, so I won't be sending you off.

553
00:34:32,080 --> 00:34:34,310
Don't worry about me. I have my son-in-law.

554
00:34:34,310 --> 00:34:36,690
Yes, I'm here. Don't worry.

555
00:34:36,690 --> 00:34:38,740
Bye.

556
00:34:38,740 --> 00:34:41,830
- Huan Er. 
 - Grandma.

557
00:34:42,690 --> 00:34:44,390
I will miss you.

558
00:34:44,390 --> 00:34:46,744
I will call you. Take good care of yourself.

559
00:34:46,744 --> 00:34:49,060
Sure, don't worry.

560
00:34:49,060 --> 00:34:50,270
Mom.

561
00:34:50,270 --> 00:34:52,830
You must pay attention to your health.

562
00:34:52,830 --> 00:34:56,190
And if you're not feeling well, let me know.

563
00:34:56,190 --> 00:34:58,670
I'll go back to visit you if I have time.

564
00:34:58,670 --> 00:34:59,750
Sure.

565
00:34:59,750 --> 00:35:01,320
Take good care of yourself too.

566
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:04,830
- Don't worry. 
 - Don't let me worry.

567
00:35:05,750 --> 00:35:07,360
Bye.

568
00:35:08,456 --> 00:35:10,460
Huan Er, no need to see me off.

569
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:12,270
- Dad, let me see you guys off. 
 - All right.

570
00:35:12,270 --> 00:35:15,290
Your grandma said no, so don't come out.

571
00:35:15,290 --> 00:35:19,160
Dad, be safe.

572
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:20,597
Go back inside.

573
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:53,920
Mom, stop crying.

574
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:55,140
You're wasting water.

575
00:35:55,140 --> 00:35:57,620
I'm not crying.

576
00:36:26,170 --> 00:36:28,060
Well...

577
00:36:28,060 --> 00:36:30,650
Don't be nervous about the operation tomorrow.

578
00:36:30,650 --> 00:36:32,440
The test results will be fine.

579
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:35,540
I'm not nervous. You're the one who's nervous.

580
00:36:35,540 --> 00:36:37,060
Why would I be nervous?

581
00:36:37,060 --> 00:36:38,390
You're nervous.

582
00:36:38,390 --> 00:36:42,840
Look. Even your hands are sweating. Look, it's all sweat.

583
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:44,510
Sweat...

584
00:36:45,270 --> 00:36:46,650
All right.

585
00:36:46,650 --> 00:36:48,320
It's late.

586
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:49,960
Go home.

587
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:51,190
There's no rush.

588
00:36:51,190 --> 00:36:54,390
- People will see you. 
 - Let me stay with you for a while longer.

589
00:36:54,390 --> 00:36:56,310
Here.

590
00:36:57,820 --> 00:36:59,940
Gosh.

591
00:37:25,790 --> 00:37:28,510
You're here.

592
00:37:36,544 --> 00:37:38,388
How did it go?

593
00:37:40,870 --> 00:37:42,620
We don't know yet.

594
00:37:42,620 --> 00:37:50,110
They'll need to do the tests after surgery to confirm the final result.

595
00:37:57,560 --> 00:38:00,079
You must have starved the whole day.

596
00:38:00,079 --> 00:38:01,691
Have some food.

597
00:38:03,910 --> 00:38:05,610
Thank you.

598
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:23,140
Don't put too much pressure on yourself.

599
00:38:23,844 --> 00:38:26,124
It isn't your fault.

600
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:29,850
Aunt Li Na will be fine.

601
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:43,800
   

602
00:39:47,980 --> 00:39:50,480
   

603
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:56,670
How did it go?

604
00:39:56,670 --> 00:39:58,376
Yi Fan, why are you here?

605
00:39:58,376 --> 00:40:01,280
I should be here. We're family. How long has she been in there?

606
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:03,060
It's been a long time. I don't know either. 
    

607
00:40:03,060 --> 00:40:05,304
- It's over. 
 - It's over, Dad.

608
00:40:05,304 --> 00:40:07,960
- This door... 
 - No rush. It'll be over soon.

609
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:09,197
- Doctor. 
 - Doctor.

610
00:40:09,197 --> 00:40:10,980
- How did it go? 
 - Everything went well.

611
00:40:10,980 --> 00:40:12,910
Family members can wait in the ward.

612
00:40:12,910 --> 00:40:15,732
Judging from the tumor removed, there should be no problem.

613
00:40:15,732 --> 00:40:17,928
But we still have to wait for the biopsy results.

614
00:40:17,928 --> 00:40:19,656
All right. Thank you.

615
00:40:19,656 --> 00:40:21,350
- Thank you, Doctor. 
 - Don't mention it. Go.

616
00:40:21,350 --> 00:40:23,128
- Thank you. 
 - Okay.

617
00:40:24,230 --> 00:40:26,760
Dad, she's fine.

618
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:28,867
Look, I told you it's a minor operation.

619
00:40:28,867 --> 00:40:31,710
Yet you still came to accompany me. You make me very nervous.

620
00:40:31,710 --> 00:40:34,330
- Uncle. 
 - I... I'll buy you some drinks.

621
00:40:34,330 --> 00:40:35,808
- No need, Uncle. No. 
 - No need. Stand here.

622
00:40:35,808 --> 00:40:38,072
- It's okay. 
 - There's no need.

623
00:40:43,750 --> 00:40:46,000
 Dad is still the same as before. 

624
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:49,310
 The more nervous he is, the more he acts like he doesn't care. 

625
00:40:49,310 --> 00:40:53,770
 I don't know if it's to comfort others or himself. 

626
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:58,740
- Slow down. 
 - Mom, slow down.

627
00:40:58,740 --> 00:41:00,270
- It's okay. 
 - Slow down.

628
00:41:00,270 --> 00:41:01,980
- It's okay. 
 - Let Huan Er help you.

629
00:41:01,980 --> 00:41:04,870
Let me do it myself. I'm not a porcelain doll.

630
00:41:04,870 --> 00:41:06,560
Jeez.

631
00:41:10,150 --> 00:41:12,460
Hey, honey.

632
00:41:12,460 --> 00:41:14,040
Xi Chi is capable.

633
00:41:14,040 --> 00:41:16,700
Doesn't he look like our son-in-law?

634
00:41:19,230 --> 00:41:22,100
Son-in-law? Stop playing matchmaker.

635
00:41:22,100 --> 00:41:24,520
He's handsome and has no shortage of girlfriends.

636
00:41:24,520 --> 00:41:26,420
They're just good friends.

637
00:41:26,420 --> 00:41:28,610
What son-in-law?

638
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:31,316
Xi Chi.

639
00:41:31,316 --> 00:41:33,320
Sorry to have bothered you recently.

640
00:41:33,320 --> 00:41:35,200
I can't take care of you all for now.

641
00:41:35,200 --> 00:41:36,820
You two will be back in school in two days.

642
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:39,331
Can I ask you to look after Huan'er on the road?

643
00:41:39,331 --> 00:41:42,070
Aunt Li Na, don't worry. Leave Chen Huan Er to me.

644
00:41:43,270 --> 00:41:44,610
Here, get up.

645
00:41:44,610 --> 00:41:48,830
- I'll do it myself. Don't touch me. 
 - Let me.

646
00:41:48,830 --> 00:41:50,100
Okay, go.

647
00:41:50,100 --> 00:41:51,310
Don't force yourself.

648
00:41:51,310 --> 00:41:55,824
- Don't touch me. Let me do it myself. 
 - I know. Let me help you.

